snippet.title: Super Smash Bros. Ultimate - New Content Approaching - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
New content approaches! Joker joins the playable roster, and updates in Ver. 3.0 include additional functionality, such as a stage builder, video editing, and Smash World integration.

Learn more about the Super Smash Bros. Ultimate Fighters Pass! https://bit.ly/2Gr8ZXj
